categories: Category:Members of the Acolytes of the Beyond

nodes.text: A young woman was a member of the Acolytes of the Beyond who traveled along with two other members to the planet Taris to purchase a lightsaber they believed belonged to Darth Vader. After buying the weapon from a Kubaz named Ooblamon, the woman claimed they would destroy the lightsaber so that it could be returned to its master in death.
